        "content": "<p>In the code below, I was expecting <code>Nat.zero2</code> to \"just work\".  Is this a misunderstanding on my part?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\">-- Only if you comment at least one of the following two commands...</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">namespace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">zero1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">zero</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\">-- ... this works</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">zero2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">zero</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">section</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">zero3</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">zero</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"c1\">-- for this to work, commenting `Nat.zero1` is inconsequential</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">end</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 470489957,
        "sender_full_name": "Damiano Testa",
        "timestamp": 1726472607
    },
    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">namespace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">zero1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">zero2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">zero</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">end</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>this is really weird</p>",
