    {
        "content": "<p>This works:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">namespace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">zero1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"n\">root_</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">zero2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">zero</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">end</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">X</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>So the <code>open Nat</code> seems to open the namespace <code>X.Nat</code> (which only exists because of the <code>def</code> of <code>zero1</code>).</p>",
        "id": 470525140,
        "sender_full_name": "Jannis Limperg",
        "timestamp": 1726479097
